# Frontend design

Follow `.cursor/skills/easycourse-design/SKILL.md`.

Quick checks before shipping UI changes:

- No `glass`, `gradient-text`, `pulse-glow`, or `btn-hover` classes
- No purple accents outside AI-specific pages/components
- Primary green used sparingly (CTA, active nav, success)
- Prefer `.surface` over blur/translucent panels
- Flat buttons; no gradient + glow shadows on cards
